WEBVTT

00:00:56.388 --> 00:00:57.666
What?

00:00:57.666 --> 00:00:59.512
What are you doing here?

00:00:59.512 --> 00:01:01.085
I moved in.

00:01:01.085 --> 00:01:02.853
Thanks to someone, I got kicked out.

00:01:02.853 --> 00:01:07.157
Why move here of all places?

00:01:07.157 --> 00:01:09.343
Aejeong-dong was the cheapest.

00:01:09.343 --> 00:01:13.123
Fresh air, killer view.

00:01:14.950 --> 00:01:17.165
And someone I'd love to kill.

00:01:20.358 --> 00:01:23.009
Hey. Come eat.

00:01:23.009 --> 00:01:25.509
Yes, ma'am.

00:01:25.509 --> 00:01:28.043
Hey, move.

00:01:28.043 --> 00:01:30.736
- What? - Move!

00:01:36.995 --> 00:01:38.888
Nice landing.

00:01:41.375 --> 00:01:46.088
Looking forward to it, you jerk of a neighbor.

00:01:54.546 --> 00:01:57.359
Long time no see, Mr. Hwang.

00:02:00.599 --> 00:02:02.977
Let me do that, Grandma.

00:02:02.977 --> 00:02:05.410
- Come on... - Why are you eating here?

00:02:06.616 --> 00:02:09.293
Actually, I'm anemic.

00:02:09.293 --> 00:02:12.864
The doctor said I'm badly malnourished.

00:02:12.864 --> 00:02:14.974
What a pity.

00:02:14.974 --> 00:02:16.054
Oh, spare me.

00:02:16.054 --> 00:02:17.974
Have a seat.

00:02:17.974 --> 00:02:20.914
Her mom even made seaweed soup.

00:02:20.914 --> 00:02:23.434
Would you like to try the soup?

00:02:30.466 --> 00:02:32.264
It's salty as hell.

00:02:32.264 --> 00:02:35.385
Did you scoop this out of the ocean?

00:02:35.385 --> 00:02:36.076
No way...

00:02:36.076 --> 00:02:37.587
- Good grief. - Water, please.

00:02:37.587 --> 00:02:39.436
She's practically Gordon Ramsay.

00:02:39.436 --> 00:02:42.311
No wonder you're all skin and bones.

00:02:44.051 --> 00:02:45.628
Hey.

00:02:45.628 --> 00:02:48.158
Eat with us from now on.

00:02:48.158 --> 00:02:51.468
It's the least I can do for the watch.

00:02:51.468 --> 00:02:54.648
In this economy? Two more mouths to feed?

00:02:54.648 --> 00:02:57.252
How much do you think office workers make?

00:02:57.252 --> 00:03:00.998
I'll pay 500,000 won a month for meals.

00:03:00.998 --> 00:03:03.342
Teach me to cook, too.

00:03:03.342 --> 00:03:05.651
I'll be your student.

00:03:05.651 --> 00:03:08.093
Looks like I got a side gig.

00:03:09.732 --> 00:03:11.432
Good for you!

00:03:12.297 --> 00:03:14.703
- I'm not eating! - What?

00:03:14.703 --> 00:03:16.607
Two freeloaders at once?

00:03:16.607 --> 00:03:20.315
What's gotten into him lately?

00:03:20.315 --> 00:03:22.368
Thanks for the meal.

00:03:23.330 --> 00:03:26.297
- Thank you, Grandma. - Sure.

00:03:32.474 --> 00:03:34.027
What now?

00:03:35.487 --> 00:03:38.871
Thanks to you, I sold my car.

00:03:38.871 --> 00:03:42.721
A decent man takes responsibility, right?

00:03:42.721 --> 00:03:46.187
What, trying to plant a bug in my car?

00:03:47.004 --> 00:03:49.168
What are you talking about?

00:03:49.168 --> 00:03:51.803
I know you moved in to dig up dirt on me.

00:03:51.803 --> 00:03:53.481
But that won't work.

00:03:53.481 --> 00:03:55.866
Stop wasting your time and move out.

00:03:55.866 --> 00:03:57.719
What, you own the place now?

00:03:57.719 --> 00:03:59.479
Yeah. I bought it.

00:04:01.021 --> 00:04:03.412
- When? - Just now.

00:04:03.412 --> 00:04:06.648
Check with the realtor. Then pack up.

00:04:08.421 --> 00:04:12.772
Is this some power trip? I have a lease, you know.

00:04:12.772 --> 00:04:14.486
Sue me if you can afford it.

00:04:14.486 --> 00:04:17.459
Two weeks. Be out by month's end.

00:04:19.578 --> 00:04:22.134
Better run for the subway.

00:04:24.470 --> 00:04:25.776
Darn it!

00:04:37.148 --> 00:04:40.415
Why does it take over an hour to get here?

00:04:42.682 --> 00:04:44.502
Good morning...

00:04:52.202 --> 00:04:53.748
Or not.

00:04:54.901 --> 00:04:58.792
Kang Bang Geul. You must have no sense of urgency.

00:04:58.792 --> 00:05:01.472
You're the last one in.

00:05:01.472 --> 00:05:02.745
That little...

00:05:06.368 --> 00:05:10.121
I'll be more careful.

00:05:12.872 --> 00:05:15.072
Where are you going?

00:05:18.044 --> 00:05:21.662
I need to get to my desk.

00:05:21.662 --> 00:05:23.692
I have returns for Materials Team.

00:05:23.692 --> 00:05:26.042
And CS complaints from the customer center.

00:05:26.042 --> 00:05:29.522
I also have contractor bids to collect.

00:05:29.522 --> 00:05:32.505
I'm busy helping other teams.

00:05:33.585 --> 00:05:36.507
That's internal work.

00:05:36.507 --> 00:05:39.892
The Future Business Team has its own orders.

00:05:40.951 --> 00:05:43.516
It's a brand-new team with nothing set up.

00:05:43.516 --> 00:05:45.377
And you have orders already?

00:05:45.377 --> 00:05:47.729
Team Leader Hwang?

00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:56.648
This is all fake muscle.

00:05:56.648 --> 00:05:58.707
I'm really weak.

00:05:58.707 --> 00:06:00.684
My back's been bad lately.

00:06:00.684 --> 00:06:03.130
No whining, everyone.

00:06:03.877 --> 00:06:05.017
My gosh.

00:06:41.610 --> 00:06:43.536
Go ahead!

00:06:53.531 --> 00:06:55.844
<i>Manage the Jungil-dong site.</i>

00:06:58.131 --> 00:07:00.510
Put your back into it.

00:07:00.510 --> 00:07:02.065
It's not working.

00:07:06.374 --> 00:07:07.832
Look at you.

00:07:07.832 --> 00:07:09.669
You've dug before, huh?

00:07:09.669 --> 00:07:11.830
No. My first time.

00:07:11.830 --> 00:07:15.906
With this strength, I could bury someone, right?

00:07:27.574 --> 00:07:31.401
<i>Handle the Choiseong Solutions shareholders' meeting.</i>

00:07:33.398 --> 00:07:35.902
Set them up nicely.

00:07:37.929 --> 00:07:39.375
And this one...

00:07:45.423 --> 00:07:47.789
You should be careful.

00:07:48.855 --> 00:07:50.827
I haul packages all day.

00:07:50.827 --> 00:07:53.548
Then calls from customers come flooding in.

00:07:53.548 --> 00:07:57.694
I get cursed out, then apologize like crazy.

00:07:57.694 --> 00:08:00.706
Now I'm a copy machine master too.

00:08:00.706 --> 00:08:02.663
You know what people call us?

00:08:02.663 --> 00:08:04.480
The Executive Contingency Team.

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:06.470
Short for the "Ex-Con Team."

00:08:06.470 --> 00:08:13.270
Now I feel guilty for no reason. Even sirens make my heart race.

00:08:13.270 --> 00:08:16.816
God, why is life so hard?

00:08:18.469 --> 00:08:21.784
I miss my wife and kids in Canada.

00:08:24.608 --> 00:08:26.472
Aren't you tired too?

00:08:26.472 --> 00:08:30.233
Mrs. Jo must be struggling with all these changes.

00:08:30.233 --> 00:08:33.053
Why not go back to the States?

00:08:33.053 --> 00:08:35.604
- I'll find you a place... - No.

00:08:35.604 --> 00:08:38.090
I'm not tired at all.

00:08:40.292 --> 00:08:41.605
Geez.

00:08:52.923 --> 00:08:55.009
What now?

00:08:58.423 --> 00:08:59.688
See?

00:08:59.688 --> 00:09:02.060
<i>Assist Finance.</i>

00:09:02.060 --> 00:09:06.053
Just thinking about that jerk fires me right up.

00:09:16.112 --> 00:09:18.194
[Sinhyup Bank]

00:09:20.126 --> 00:09:23.072
- How can I help you? - I need to withdraw cash.

00:09:35.282 --> 00:09:38.620
This tint is the hottest one right now.

00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:40.803
Shade 06, Cherry.

00:09:40.803 --> 00:09:45.063
Buy it with that card, and you get instant cashback.

00:09:45.828 --> 00:09:49.460
Use that debit card, and you get cashback on coffee too.

00:09:49.460 --> 00:09:51.886
Would you like to apply?

00:09:59.763 --> 00:10:02.873
Bang Geul won't give up.

00:10:02.873 --> 00:10:04.797
Enough nonsense.

00:10:04.797 --> 00:10:07.817
Make her quit.

00:10:07.817 --> 00:10:10.883
And keep her away from Jae Gyeong.

00:10:11.501 --> 00:10:13.611
This will only make things worse between you and her.

00:10:13.611 --> 00:10:17.507
She hates every word that starts with "Hwang."

00:10:17.507 --> 00:10:21.545
What about Professor Min? Any movement from him?

00:10:22.376 --> 00:10:24.647
He resigned.

00:10:24.647 --> 00:10:26.783
Rumor says he's joining Choiseong.

00:10:26.783 --> 00:10:30.053
He's basically saying that he's an accomplice.

00:10:31.954 --> 00:10:33.713
<i>Who are you?</i>

00:10:34.590 --> 00:10:37.831
Use this video to pressure Jae Gyeong.

00:10:37.831 --> 00:10:39.989
She was the last person to visit the room that day.

00:10:39.989 --> 00:10:42.429
It doesn't prove she killed him.

00:10:42.429 --> 00:10:44.613
It's not enough.

00:10:44.613 --> 00:10:46.513
What else?

00:10:47.473 --> 00:10:51.203
The CCTV went down during a security check.

00:10:51.203 --> 00:10:54.402
The staffer got the date wrong.

00:10:54.402 --> 00:10:56.649
[Personnel Record Card] The hospital let it slide.

00:10:56.649 --> 00:11:00.316
Jae Gyeong must've pulled strings.

00:11:00.316 --> 00:11:02.519
So where is he now?

00:11:07.382 --> 00:11:08.946
<i>Good, good.</i>

00:11:08.946 --> 00:11:11.379
<i>Time to turn my life around.</i>

00:11:17.433 --> 00:11:20.125
He's been out sick for days.

00:11:20.125 --> 00:11:23.174
[Personnel Record Card] He asked for big money, then went dark?

00:11:23.174 --> 00:11:24.758
Find him fast.

00:11:24.758 --> 00:11:26.968
- Before this blows up. - Got it.

00:11:26.968 --> 00:11:29.968
I'm checking his home, family, and friends.

00:11:38.023 --> 00:11:41.787
The department heads are complaining.

00:11:41.787 --> 00:11:43.693
Aren't you pushing them too hard?

00:11:43.693 --> 00:11:46.777
Results matter most right after taking office.

00:11:46.777 --> 00:11:49.265
Everyone should stay sharp.

00:11:49.265 --> 00:11:50.400
Oh, right.

00:11:50.400 --> 00:11:52.882
Taeha contacted us.

00:11:52.882 --> 00:11:56.606
They want the Daesan hydrogen complex settled by next week.

00:11:56.606 --> 00:11:59.276
They want to collect their cut?

00:12:00.269 --> 00:12:02.582
Secretary Yeo, handle that.

00:12:03.823 --> 00:12:05.866
Don't worry about it.

00:12:05.866 --> 00:12:07.706
Yes, ma'am.

00:12:26.205 --> 00:12:29.085
I think Jae Gyeong is hiding the security staffer.

00:12:29.085 --> 00:12:32.361
- We need to get to him first. <i>- I found him.</i>

00:12:32.361 --> 00:12:35.640
Do you trust Hwang Jun Hyeon?

00:12:36.795 --> 00:12:39.272
Well...

00:12:39.272 --> 00:12:42.044
He does things just right.

00:12:42.044 --> 00:12:44.828
<i>Bang Geul moved in next door to me.</i>

00:12:44.828 --> 00:12:47.575
<i>I think she's digging around. What should I do?</i>

00:12:47.575 --> 00:12:51.212
<i>I told you to handle those two.</i>

00:12:51.212 --> 00:12:52.795
<i>So handle it.</i>

00:12:52.795 --> 00:12:58.121
<i>As promised, I'll send them to the States this month.</i>

00:13:00.018 --> 00:13:01.930
But still...

00:13:03.311 --> 00:13:06.148
What's that old man's angle?

00:13:06.148 --> 00:13:07.154
[Chairman Na Byeong Mo]

00:13:15.960 --> 00:13:17.960
Tell Taeha this.

00:13:18.613 --> 00:13:22.804
If they don't hand over the money and shares this week,

00:13:22.804 --> 00:13:27.164
They'll never get the core hydrogen technology.

00:13:32.218 --> 00:13:33.971
This is nuts.

00:13:43.580 --> 00:13:44.704
[Moneybags]

00:13:44.704 --> 00:13:47.537
Let them sweat a little more.

00:13:49.687 --> 00:13:51.487
<i>Secretary Yeo?</i>

00:14:08.250 --> 00:14:09.929
- Damn it! - Oh my.

00:14:10.627 --> 00:14:11.962
I'm so sorry.

00:14:11.962 --> 00:14:13.995
Are you kidding me?

00:14:13.995 --> 00:14:16.458
- I'm sorry. - What the...

00:14:17.515 --> 00:14:21.455
Here. Dry-cleaning and medical bills.

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:25.280
You think money solves everything?

00:14:26.576 --> 00:14:29.302
And extra for a bath and all that.

00:14:30.527 --> 00:14:31.758
Sir!

00:14:31.758 --> 00:14:34.717
One more ramen, please. And clean this up.

00:14:34.717 --> 00:14:37.450
- Thank you. - Sorry again.

00:14:42.317 --> 00:14:44.342
[Birthdate] [Phone Number] 8-2-7-2...

00:14:44.342 --> 00:14:46.801
1-0-1-2...

00:14:56.646 --> 00:14:58.072
[Moneybags]

00:15:04.526 --> 00:15:06.303
<i>10 p.m.</i>

00:15:06.303 --> 00:15:08.427
<i>Under Sehwa Bridge. Parking lot.</i>

00:15:08.427 --> 00:15:10.156
<i>500 million won.</i>

00:15:13.189 --> 00:15:14.388
[Okay]

00:15:30.302 --> 00:15:31.538
How did it go?

00:15:31.538 --> 00:15:33.841
We'll pay what he wants.

00:15:33.841 --> 00:15:35.587
Let's wait a bit.

00:15:37.088 --> 00:15:38.947
What about Taeha?

00:15:38.947 --> 00:15:42.277
It seems like they're dodging us on purpose.

00:15:42.277 --> 00:15:44.870
Secretary Jo won't take my calls.

00:15:50.339 --> 00:15:55.900
That can't be what Chairman Na is counting on, huh?

00:16:20.711 --> 00:16:22.411
What's he doing here?

00:16:26.768 --> 00:16:28.304
[Moneybags]

00:16:33.018 --> 00:16:35.977
That bastard, Na Byeong Mo.

00:16:44.036 --> 00:16:46.400
- Anything? - No one's here.

00:16:46.400 --> 00:16:48.540
- Let's check his place. - Yes, sir.

00:17:19.071 --> 00:17:21.147
The staffer vanished?

00:17:21.147 --> 00:17:22.966
I was too late.

00:17:22.966 --> 00:17:25.972
His place was trashed. Nothing useful.

00:17:26.820 --> 00:17:30.424
How could she work with Chairman Na?

00:17:30.424 --> 00:17:34.423
She knows how much you hated him.

00:17:34.423 --> 00:17:36.545
No.

00:17:36.545 --> 00:17:39.653
Something's off.

00:17:39.653 --> 00:17:44.148
She'd never let Chairman Na near her weakness.

00:17:44.148 --> 00:17:45.901
Then...

00:17:48.421 --> 00:17:51.885
Chairman Na is blackmailing Jae Gyeong?

00:17:51.885 --> 00:17:53.909
He figured it out.

00:17:53.909 --> 00:17:56.466
He knows Jae Gyeong killed me.

00:17:57.133 --> 00:17:59.815
That's why he wanted the CCTV.

00:17:59.815 --> 00:18:05.112
If he gets it, he'll use it to deal with Choiseong.

00:18:05.112 --> 00:18:10.009
Then isn't it better if Jae Gyeong has him?

00:18:10.009 --> 00:18:13.495
Then she'll destroy the evidence.

00:18:16.053 --> 00:18:18.372
We have one thing left.

00:18:20.601 --> 00:18:24.493
Let's hope this phone has proof that she is the killer.

00:18:24.493 --> 00:18:26.329
[Tip: The suspicious death of Chairman Kang]

00:18:29.842 --> 00:18:32.148
Hayoung Daily got a tip.

00:18:34.306 --> 00:18:36.865
I stopped the article from going out.

00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:44.661
If there's a tip, someone else suspects Jae Gyeong too.

00:18:44.661 --> 00:18:48.887
Then there's CCTV from the hospital on the day Father collapsed.

00:18:48.887 --> 00:18:51.405
Proof that Jae Gyeong is the real killer.

00:18:51.405 --> 00:18:53.802
What about the tipster? It's your friend's paper.

00:18:53.802 --> 00:18:55.617
It was anonymous.

00:18:55.617 --> 00:18:59.519
But that punk seems to be hiding something.

00:19:00.279 --> 00:19:02.458
Hello, ma'am.

00:19:06.771 --> 00:19:08.550
You should've called me.

00:19:08.550 --> 00:19:12.159
You didn't have to come all the way here.

00:19:13.871 --> 00:19:15.404
Hey.

00:19:16.944 --> 00:19:19.262
Did you meet the CEO of Hayoung Daily?

00:19:19.262 --> 00:19:21.892
Hayoung Daily?

00:19:21.892 --> 00:19:23.270
Jeong Hak Hui?

00:19:23.270 --> 00:19:26.096
I barely talk to him these days.

00:19:26.096 --> 00:19:28.173
Don't play dumb.

00:19:28.173 --> 00:19:30.609
I know you two are close.

00:19:31.836 --> 00:19:34.136
Did he say anything?

00:19:34.876 --> 00:19:36.353
About what?

00:19:36.353 --> 00:19:38.406
Did some article come out?

00:19:39.069 --> 00:19:40.662
Hey.

00:19:41.506 --> 00:19:46.019
If you and Bang Geul are hiding something from me,

00:19:47.065 --> 00:19:49.558
You'll lose this seat.

00:20:02.852 --> 00:20:06.938
Why bring up that awful name?

00:20:28.423 --> 00:20:31.627
Hey, answer your phone.

00:20:31.627 --> 00:20:33.600
It sounds important.

00:20:50.373 --> 00:20:52.530
You weren't in your office, so I came...

00:20:52.530 --> 00:20:54.910
Later, Mr. Hwang.

00:21:00.375 --> 00:21:04.141
Guess traitors don't get looped in.

00:21:07.502 --> 00:21:11.367
She got a call and stormed off looking furious.

00:21:11.367 --> 00:21:14.707
- Was it about the tip? - What tip?

00:21:14.707 --> 00:21:19.071
I thought Jae Gyeong adored you. Guess you're out of the loop.

00:21:19.071 --> 00:21:21.009
Then spell it out.

00:21:21.009 --> 00:21:25.545
A newspaper got a tip that Jae Gyeong killed my dad.

00:21:25.545 --> 00:21:30.140
The dead CCTV caught her face plain as day.

00:21:31.453 --> 00:21:33.925
Crime has a way of catching up.

00:21:33.925 --> 00:21:36.370
The truth always comes out.

00:21:36.370 --> 00:21:38.568
Hayoung Daily, right?

00:21:38.568 --> 00:21:40.705
Did Jae Seong show you the article?

00:21:40.705 --> 00:21:43.185
What was on the CCTV?

00:21:43.185 --> 00:21:44.615
What photo of her?

00:21:44.615 --> 00:21:46.949
You're not asking the most important thing.

00:21:46.949 --> 00:21:50.422
You know who the tipster is, don't you?

00:21:51.455 --> 00:21:57.309
The tipster has proof that she killed my dad, right?

00:21:58.883 --> 00:22:01.110
Hey.

00:22:01.110 --> 00:22:04.689
Stop playing detective.

00:22:05.293 --> 00:22:08.247
There's nothing you can do.

00:22:12.487 --> 00:22:14.565
That jerk...

00:22:14.565 --> 00:22:16.811
Jae Seong.

00:22:16.811 --> 00:22:19.674
I think Jun Hyeon knows the tipster.

00:22:19.674 --> 00:22:22.287
Could it be someone around us?

00:22:54.764 --> 00:22:58.844
Look at this one. Full of roe.

00:22:58.844 --> 00:23:02.055
Eat it whole. That's the best part.

00:23:02.055 --> 00:23:03.629
What did you want to say?

00:23:03.629 --> 00:23:06.155
Always in a rush.

00:23:16.715 --> 00:23:23.360
Transfer the Daesan Hydrogen Complex core tech with no final payment.

00:23:28.556 --> 00:23:30.143
[Hydrogen Complex Transfer Agreement]

00:23:31.663 --> 00:23:33.976
I never agreed to this crap.

00:23:35.592 --> 00:23:37.923
Then leave Choiseong.

00:23:37.923 --> 00:23:41.130
- I'll kindly take you in. - Chairman Na!

00:23:41.130 --> 00:23:45.553
Don't you raise your voice. You killed your own father.

00:23:54.025 --> 00:23:56.929
Run a Taeha Energy ad in Hayoung Daily.

00:23:56.929 --> 00:24:00.212
CEO Jeong did good work.

00:24:00.212 --> 00:24:01.899
Yes, sir.

00:24:02.855 --> 00:24:04.952
So it was you?

00:24:04.952 --> 00:24:06.319
You framed me?

00:24:06.319 --> 00:24:09.479
"Framed you?" It's the truth.

00:24:11.425 --> 00:24:14.566
I should never have dealt with trash like you.

00:24:16.312 --> 00:24:24.401
<i>At first, we planned to use Professor Min's sleeping pills.</i>

00:24:24.401 --> 00:24:31.961
<i>But Father opened his eyes, so she smothered him with a pillow.</i>

00:24:32.734 --> 00:24:35.658
<i>Did he say I ordered him to do it?</i>

00:24:35.658 --> 00:24:39.605
<i>Or did he say he only pretended to?</i>

00:24:39.605 --> 00:24:42.375
<i>Your husband is an accomplice too.</i>

00:24:42.375 --> 00:24:45.558
<i>Let's see whose crime is worse.</i>

00:24:53.679 --> 00:24:56.405
That recording proves nothing.

00:24:56.405 --> 00:24:58.180
You think people will buy that?

00:24:58.180 --> 00:25:03.492
You cremated your father, won over the board, and took the chairman's seat.

00:25:03.492 --> 00:25:05.770
Even your family suspects you.

00:25:05.770 --> 00:25:09.373
- Who would believe you? - Don't twist this.

00:25:09.373 --> 00:25:13.139
My father was alive when I left!

00:25:15.993 --> 00:25:18.050
<i>Who are you?</i>

00:25:22.103 --> 00:25:27.063
<i>You sure are hard to kill.</i>

00:25:34.406 --> 00:25:35.804
It wasn't me.

00:25:35.804 --> 00:25:37.864
I didn't kill him!

00:25:38.714 --> 00:25:40.600
Wait.

00:25:41.627 --> 00:25:43.467
Did you kill my father?

00:25:43.467 --> 00:25:48.305
You never cared whether he died or someone killed him.

00:25:48.305 --> 00:25:50.905
Now you're curious?

00:25:53.224 --> 00:25:58.761
Kang Yong Ho died at the hands of his daughter.

00:25:58.761 --> 00:26:01.221
I'll make sure of that.

00:26:02.221 --> 00:26:04.785
What are you, God?

00:26:04.785 --> 00:26:06.641
How will you hide the truth?

00:26:06.641 --> 00:26:09.307
Yeah, you can't hide it.

00:26:12.136 --> 00:26:14.175
So you erase it.

00:26:23.997 --> 00:26:26.694
He contacted you too, right?

00:26:26.694 --> 00:26:30.056
Said he'd tell you the truth if you paid enough.

00:26:34.229 --> 00:26:37.042
He got too greedy.

00:27:43.263 --> 00:27:45.911
[Kang Jae Gyeong]

00:27:49.005 --> 00:27:51.491
Yes, ma'am.

00:27:52.431 --> 00:27:54.464
Where are you?

00:28:06.074 --> 00:28:08.074
[The Late Kang Yong Ho]

00:28:16.963 --> 00:28:19.923
Are you hiding something from me?

00:28:23.554 --> 00:28:27.122
I read the tip Secretary Yeo sent.

00:28:27.122 --> 00:28:32.081
Did you... really kill him?

00:28:33.428 --> 00:28:36.154
Don't get cocky.

00:28:37.868 --> 00:28:41.798
Did you kill your own father?

00:28:41.798 --> 00:28:43.917
I said shut up!

00:28:55.510 --> 00:28:59.370
If this is your weakness, we need to prepare.

00:28:59.370 --> 00:29:01.370
Answer me.

00:29:05.000 --> 00:29:07.261
Na Byeong Mo did it.

00:29:07.261 --> 00:29:09.747
He's trying to frame me.

00:29:10.537 --> 00:29:13.614
He got me good.

00:29:13.614 --> 00:29:16.297
Chairman Na killed him?

00:29:17.148 --> 00:29:19.440
Are you sure?

00:29:21.917 --> 00:29:25.368
So now the whole world suspects me.

00:29:25.368 --> 00:29:27.060
Why would I kill Father?

00:29:27.060 --> 00:29:29.346
He was dying anyway.

00:29:29.346 --> 00:29:31.540
Choiseong was already mine. Why would I?

00:29:31.540 --> 00:29:35.153
So you had nothing to do with it?

00:29:35.153 --> 00:29:36.637
Nothing.

00:29:36.637 --> 00:29:38.967
Not a thing.

00:29:38.967 --> 00:29:41.624
Then call for a police investigation.

00:29:41.624 --> 00:29:43.206
No.

00:29:45.062 --> 00:29:48.215
If this blows up, I'll be the one cornered.

00:29:49.635 --> 00:29:54.510
Once we find proof that Chairman Na is the real killer...

00:29:54.510 --> 00:29:57.861
The tables will turn.

00:29:57.861 --> 00:30:02.064
I'll pay him back for today's humiliation.

00:30:02.064 --> 00:30:04.721
I'll save Choiseong and get revenge.

00:30:04.721 --> 00:30:07.694
Then Father can rest in peace.

00:30:09.832 --> 00:30:13.417
Is that what he'd want?

00:30:13.417 --> 00:30:15.753
Then what does he want?

00:30:17.241 --> 00:30:20.591
He should've died quietly.

00:30:20.591 --> 00:30:23.855
That selfish old man.

00:30:23.855 --> 00:30:26.380
I'm settling his grudge.

00:30:26.380 --> 00:30:28.704
What's wrong with that?

00:30:32.435 --> 00:30:35.248
Should I find it for you?

00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:39.399
Proof that Chairman Na killed your father.

00:30:39.399 --> 00:30:42.562
The hospital CCTV is gone.

00:30:42.562 --> 00:30:44.039
The witness is dead.

00:30:44.039 --> 00:30:46.996
Then we make some.

00:30:46.996 --> 00:30:49.132
I told you.

00:30:50.282 --> 00:30:52.859
I'm with you to the end.

00:30:55.049 --> 00:31:02.569
Tell me everything that happened with Chairman Na.

00:31:41.079 --> 00:31:42.736
- You're here. - Yeah.

00:31:42.736 --> 00:31:44.899
- This way, please. - Okay.

00:31:55.123 --> 00:31:57.277
Why is he here?

00:32:13.356 --> 00:32:16.929
This office gets great sun.

00:32:21.863 --> 00:32:25.321
You should finish the Daesan Hydrogen Complex deal.

00:32:25.321 --> 00:32:30.334
Please settle the 100 billion balance as agreed.

00:32:31.608 --> 00:32:35.241
I'm asking you.

00:32:38.661 --> 00:32:43.024
Maybe I should've played the recording in the meeting.

00:32:43.024 --> 00:32:46.317
A lot of people there miss Kang Yong Ho.

00:32:47.691 --> 00:32:50.430
I'm kidding.

00:32:51.718 --> 00:32:56.955
But getting here wasn't easy for me either.

00:32:56.955 --> 00:32:59.415
I lost a lot too.

00:33:00.483 --> 00:33:02.445
So cover my losses.

00:33:02.445 --> 00:33:05.898
You have money tucked away, huh?

00:33:05.898 --> 00:33:08.638
What was it called? Siren?

00:33:09.797 --> 00:33:12.587
Since I'm here, I'll look around Choiseong.

00:33:12.587 --> 00:33:14.770
Don't mind me.

00:33:15.550 --> 00:33:17.930
Get back to work.

00:33:47.982 --> 00:33:49.824
[Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong]

00:33:49.824 --> 00:33:53.501
I thought it'd be good for you all to meet.

00:33:53.501 --> 00:33:58.516
Taeha and Choiseong will be doing more together.

00:33:58.516 --> 00:34:01.281
Let's be clear.

00:34:01.281 --> 00:34:03.806
I'm here to help.

00:34:03.806 --> 00:34:08.705
Sitting in that chair isn't everything.

00:34:08.705 --> 00:34:11.450
Choiseong has no elder now.

00:34:13.463 --> 00:34:14.934
CEO Hyun.

00:34:14.934 --> 00:34:20.870
I hear Choiseong Distribution's logistics system is top-notch.

00:34:20.870 --> 00:34:24.127
Taeha wants to grow that side too.

00:34:24.127 --> 00:34:26.747
We could do better together.

00:34:28.500 --> 00:34:33.266
Have you discussed this with Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong?

00:34:34.538 --> 00:34:38.175
You can discuss it over dinner.

00:34:38.175 --> 00:34:40.648
Taeha will host you today.

00:34:43.780 --> 00:34:48.945
Chairman Na and his daughter had lunch with the CEOs.

00:34:48.945 --> 00:34:52.238
Even Na Eun Se is enjoying herself now.

00:34:57.006 --> 00:35:02.346
If I push them, they might leak the CCTV footage.

00:35:02.346 --> 00:35:04.827
Don't let it rattle you.

00:35:05.560 --> 00:35:09.187
You need leverage to fight back.

00:35:09.187 --> 00:35:10.217
What?

00:35:10.217 --> 00:35:13.868
Chairman Na won't show his hand yet.

00:35:13.868 --> 00:35:18.155
So hang in there.

00:35:18.902 --> 00:35:21.843
Better than losing your seat.

00:35:21.843 --> 00:35:22.890
Hwang Jun Hyeon!

00:35:22.890 --> 00:35:26.903
If you hand over the core tech for free, will the shareholders stay quiet?

00:35:26.903 --> 00:35:33.290
How will the staff see you if your first deal makes you look weak?

00:35:33.290 --> 00:35:36.811
This directly affects your leadership.

00:35:36.811 --> 00:35:40.071
Don't lecture me. Give me a plan.

00:35:40.071 --> 00:35:41.308
What do you want to do?

00:35:41.308 --> 00:35:45.518
Chairman Na threatened you with a rumor and stole the hydrogen tech without paying.

00:35:45.518 --> 00:35:48.318
That's enough to throw one jab.

00:35:49.631 --> 00:35:52.964
How will you move that vicious man?

00:35:53.850 --> 00:35:55.817
You have me.

00:35:55.817 --> 00:35:57.943
The icon of betrayal.

00:35:59.407 --> 00:36:01.611
You think Chairman Na will trust you?

00:36:01.611 --> 00:36:04.032
He'll either trust me or kill me.

00:36:04.032 --> 00:36:06.314
One or the other.

00:36:06.314 --> 00:36:09.447
Either way, you lose nothing.

00:36:17.096 --> 00:36:18.866
Secretary Yeo.

00:36:18.866 --> 00:36:22.246
From now on, follow Mr. Hwang's orders.

00:36:22.246 --> 00:36:24.746
Give him whatever he needs.

00:36:27.053 --> 00:36:30.539
I'm betting everything on you, Mr. Hwang.

00:36:40.389 --> 00:36:42.709
Chairman Na Byeong Mo?

00:36:43.590 --> 00:36:47.122
This is Hwang Jun Hyeon from Choiseong's Future Business Team.

00:36:54.285 --> 00:36:58.030
Jae Gyeong isn't the type to bow to him.

00:36:58.030 --> 00:37:01.240
Chairman Na didn't even pay the hydrogen balance.

00:37:01.240 --> 00:37:04.771
It's weird, right? She never caves like this.

00:37:04.771 --> 00:37:08.821
But the tipster is even weirder.

00:37:08.821 --> 00:37:09.959
You found out?

00:37:09.959 --> 00:37:11.655
Who is it?

00:37:11.655 --> 00:37:17.322
That punk wouldn't talk at first. Said he'd rather die.

00:37:17.322 --> 00:37:20.232
But two bottles of whiskey later...

00:37:20.232 --> 00:37:22.332
He's a lightweight.

00:37:22.332 --> 00:37:25.824
Me? I never get drunk. Just like Father.

00:37:25.824 --> 00:37:30.104
Anyway, who's the tipster?

00:37:32.823 --> 00:37:35.677
It was someone around us.

00:37:35.677 --> 00:37:36.940
Na Byeong Mo.

00:37:36.940 --> 00:37:38.159
What?

00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:40.049
Chairman Na?

00:37:40.049 --> 00:37:44.652
That vicious man offered ads worth hundreds of millions

00:37:44.652 --> 00:37:47.565
And told them not to run the article.

00:37:47.565 --> 00:37:51.622
He said to just send it to Jae Gyeong.

00:37:53.728 --> 00:37:58.268
So Jae Gyeong is being blackmailed by Chairman Na.

00:38:00.704 --> 00:38:06.003
Chairman Na likes bonsai, right?

00:38:10.044 --> 00:38:14.096
This is our bonsai expert. It wasn't easy getting her here.

00:38:15.519 --> 00:38:19.232
Chairman Na will be furious if he finds out.

00:38:20.985 --> 00:38:22.998
For your trouble.

00:38:24.293 --> 00:38:28.392
He won't be back anytime soon. Don't worry.

00:38:35.203 --> 00:38:37.340
Hard drives. External drives. USBs.

00:38:37.340 --> 00:38:39.910
- Find it all. - Got it.

00:38:39.910 --> 00:38:43.152
Hospital CCTV, the Jae Gyeong and Chairman Na connection...

00:38:43.152 --> 00:38:45.398
I'll find something.

00:38:56.693 --> 00:38:58.542
Professor Min.

00:39:00.530 --> 00:39:02.336
Mrs. Jo?

00:39:03.266 --> 00:39:07.417
I hear you're barely home lately.

00:39:07.417 --> 00:39:10.338
Il Jun called me.

00:39:10.338 --> 00:39:12.843
He said he wanted this.

00:39:13.641 --> 00:39:15.474
Please don't do this again.

00:39:15.474 --> 00:39:17.020
Or don't take his calls.

00:39:17.020 --> 00:39:18.848
That's too cruel.

00:39:18.848 --> 00:39:21.980
Please go. I'll give it to him.

00:39:23.651 --> 00:39:28.157
You did everything you could to save Chairman Kang.

00:39:28.157 --> 00:39:30.896
I know you meant it.

00:39:32.393 --> 00:39:38.573
I just want the truth about how he died.

00:39:39.994 --> 00:39:43.640
For Il Jun's sake, don't do anything you'll regret.

00:39:44.251 --> 00:39:46.785
You're a father too.

00:39:50.881 --> 00:39:53.527
Then I'll be punished.

00:40:04.707 --> 00:40:06.950
He quit the hospital.

00:40:06.950 --> 00:40:09.523
Why would he need that?

00:40:33.365 --> 00:40:37.481
There's no golf course around there.

00:40:37.481 --> 00:40:40.247
Kang Jae Gyeong, that crazy...

00:40:42.430 --> 00:40:44.621
[Supplemental Agreement on Strategic Investment]

00:40:44.621 --> 00:40:49.056
What the... She sold that precious hydrogen deal for this?

00:40:49.056 --> 00:40:50.702
Let's take it.

00:40:55.125 --> 00:40:57.243
You're done, Jae Gyeong.

00:40:57.243 --> 00:40:59.755
He is almost here!

00:40:59.755 --> 00:41:01.595
One minute!

00:41:36.665 --> 00:41:39.221
Sorry I'm late.

00:41:39.854 --> 00:41:42.539
Welcome, Mr. Hwang.

00:41:42.539 --> 00:41:44.539
Come inside.

00:41:49.674 --> 00:41:52.521
That traitor bastard...

00:41:54.822 --> 00:41:57.295
What is he up to now?

00:42:00.097 --> 00:42:03.342
You must've lost my card, so I came myself.

00:42:03.342 --> 00:42:09.081
So you meant it about making me your third master.

00:42:09.081 --> 00:42:11.999
The side I backed is going down.

00:42:11.999 --> 00:42:14.749
The rumor is everywhere.

00:42:14.749 --> 00:42:17.475
Jae Gyeong killed her father.

00:42:18.396 --> 00:42:22.499
The company is noisier now than when he died.

00:42:22.499 --> 00:42:24.816
We don't know the truth yet.

00:42:24.816 --> 00:42:30.238
Truth or not, no one follows a fallen general.

00:42:30.238 --> 00:42:33.784
Switching sides at the right time is a skill.

00:42:33.784 --> 00:42:38.282
And you seem to have real leverage over Jae Gyeong.

00:42:46.865 --> 00:42:48.865
Mr. Hwang.

00:42:49.720 --> 00:42:52.560
Do I look that easy to fool?

00:42:58.199 --> 00:43:03.415
Jae Gyeong said you killed Chairman Kang and framed her.

00:43:03.415 --> 00:43:07.935
She had no proof, so she asked for my help.

00:43:07.935 --> 00:43:10.280
Not that I believe her.

00:43:10.280 --> 00:43:12.499
Why would I?

00:43:22.390 --> 00:43:24.788
Do you know what it took to get here?

00:43:24.788 --> 00:43:28.254
She has to pay for what she did to me.

00:43:29.421 --> 00:43:33.432
Your hit-and-run... That was her?

00:43:33.432 --> 00:43:35.649
She even sold out Chairman Kang.

00:43:35.649 --> 00:43:39.275
Why would I help Jae Gyeong?

00:43:40.305 --> 00:43:44.478
She ruined a bright young man's life.

00:43:44.478 --> 00:43:47.581
As an elder, I can't ignore that.

00:43:47.581 --> 00:43:49.950
Let him go first.

00:43:49.950 --> 00:43:53.223
Let's talk about how you'll get revenge.

00:43:54.556 --> 00:43:56.195
Shall we?

00:44:01.676 --> 00:44:04.867
I'll hand over the hydrogen tech first.

00:44:04.867 --> 00:44:09.122
There's plenty more to take from Jae Gyeong.

00:44:22.454 --> 00:44:24.305
I'm impressed.

00:44:24.305 --> 00:44:26.452
Good judgment. Fast moves.

00:44:26.452 --> 00:44:28.922
No wonder everyone asks for you.

00:44:28.922 --> 00:44:30.332
I'm flattered.

00:44:31.918 --> 00:44:33.978
Careful.

00:44:35.062 --> 00:44:36.822
Thank you.

00:44:40.634 --> 00:44:42.138
Did you hurt your ankle?

00:44:42.138 --> 00:44:44.488
The pain is almost gone.

00:44:44.488 --> 00:44:47.068
But stairs still get me.

00:44:58.132 --> 00:45:01.876
Was Jae Gyeong really the only one who went to the room that day?

00:45:01.876 --> 00:45:03.689
Yes.

00:45:03.689 --> 00:45:08.609
She left the room, and soon after, Chairman Kang collapsed.

00:45:09.323 --> 00:45:11.689
Nothing unusual?

00:45:12.349 --> 00:45:14.993
Think carefully.

00:45:14.993 --> 00:45:17.526
Unusual? Well...

00:45:20.744 --> 00:45:22.367
The stairs.

00:45:22.367 --> 00:45:23.967
"The stairs?"

00:45:23.967 --> 00:45:25.974
It was odd.

00:45:25.974 --> 00:45:29.626
The elevator wasn't broken, but she took the emergency stairs.

00:45:31.866 --> 00:45:33.921
[Do Not Enter]

00:45:33.921 --> 00:45:34.925
[Stairwell]

00:45:36.133 --> 00:45:38.456
She took the stairs on purpose.

00:45:38.456 --> 00:45:41.203
She couldn't run into Jae Gyeong.

00:45:41.203 --> 00:45:42.749
What?

00:45:42.749 --> 00:45:46.469
There was someone else that day.

00:46:11.230 --> 00:46:15.443
<i>You don't think you got here on your own, do you?</i>

00:46:22.422 --> 00:46:23.908
<i>Na Byeong Mo did it.</i>

00:46:23.908 --> 00:46:25.456
<i>He's trying to frame me.</i>

00:46:28.364 --> 00:46:30.401
<i>The rumor is everywhere.</i>

00:46:30.401 --> 00:46:32.315
<i>Jae Gyeong killed her father.</i>

00:46:32.315 --> 00:46:35.401
<i>We don't know the truth yet.</i>

00:47:39.604 --> 00:47:42.217
<i>Same build as Jae Gyeong.</i>

00:47:43.457 --> 00:47:46.570
<i>She knows Jae Gyeong's style.</i>

00:47:47.744 --> 00:47:51.897
<i>She has a deep grudge against Jae Gyeong.</i>

00:47:54.709 --> 00:47:56.849
Na Eun Se.

00:47:59.995 --> 00:48:01.909
It was you.

00:48:06.976 --> 00:48:09.249
You killed me.

00:48:17.182 --> 00:48:20.087
You should've found somewhere nicer.

00:48:20.087 --> 00:48:22.036
I'll pay more, so move out.

00:48:22.036 --> 00:48:25.456
With your slush money?

00:48:25.456 --> 00:48:28.484
Jae Gyeong will lock you up again.

00:48:28.484 --> 00:48:33.045
This place is tiny. There isn't even a corner to cry in.

00:48:36.364 --> 00:48:42.276
You always hid in corners and swallowed your tears.

00:48:42.276 --> 00:48:45.695
The kitchen, the wine cellar, the garage...

00:48:45.695 --> 00:48:47.885
All because of evil Jae Gyeong...

00:48:47.885 --> 00:48:50.354
You had a part in it too.

00:48:52.235 --> 00:48:54.718
I'm sorry.

00:48:54.718 --> 00:48:56.839
I was a lousy person.

00:48:56.839 --> 00:48:59.320
I don't know why I was so immature.

00:49:02.432 --> 00:49:05.832
You say that like you're mature now.

00:49:06.627 --> 00:49:08.424
I'm not mature.

00:49:08.424 --> 00:49:11.711
But I'm good for something.

00:49:11.711 --> 00:49:13.111
- What's that? - See?

00:49:13.111 --> 00:49:15.437
I get things done.

00:49:16.612 --> 00:49:20.097
With this, Taeha can't take the hydrogen deal, huh?

00:49:20.097 --> 00:49:22.521
The side deal puts Taeha at risk.

00:49:22.521 --> 00:49:24.598
Na Byeong Mo won't even blink.

00:49:24.598 --> 00:49:27.027
It'll only drag Choiseong into a contract scandal.

00:49:27.027 --> 00:49:28.117
Still...

00:49:28.117 --> 00:49:29.544
Jae Seong is right.

00:49:29.544 --> 00:49:33.453
This doesn't prove Jae Gyeong is the killer.

00:49:34.307 --> 00:49:36.510
What about the tipster?

00:49:36.510 --> 00:49:37.816
Well, that's...

00:49:39.800 --> 00:49:44.008
I'm supposed to be malnourished, so my hands are weak.

00:49:44.008 --> 00:49:45.581
Be careful.

00:49:45.581 --> 00:49:48.427
I'll find you something to change into.

00:49:48.427 --> 00:49:49.937
What are you doing?

00:49:49.937 --> 00:49:53.977
Don't tell her anything. Not until we're sure.

00:49:53.977 --> 00:49:55.554
What do you take me for?

00:49:55.554 --> 00:49:57.761
I was going to make something up.

00:49:57.761 --> 00:50:00.251
No, you were dying to tell her.

00:50:00.251 --> 00:50:01.522
- Hide! - What?

00:50:01.522 --> 00:50:03.263
Hide!

00:50:03.263 --> 00:50:04.942
What now?

00:50:07.027 --> 00:50:09.934
- What? - Jae Gyeong's lackey is here.

00:50:18.739 --> 00:50:20.549
That bastard...

00:50:20.549 --> 00:50:23.588
Where's he been crawling around?

00:50:23.588 --> 00:50:25.949
Who did he betray this time?

00:50:25.949 --> 00:50:29.945
He must have some kind of plan. It's not betrayal.

00:50:29.945 --> 00:50:33.668
Betrayal is hard the first time. After that, it's easy.

00:50:33.668 --> 00:50:36.214
- Speaking from experience? - Hey.

00:50:39.046 --> 00:50:41.797
- Will this work? - Nice pants.

00:50:41.797 --> 00:50:44.289
Totally my style.

00:50:45.199 --> 00:50:49.613
Jun Hyeon definitely sided with Taeha. Want to bet?

00:50:49.613 --> 00:50:53.033
Bet on that? How childish.

00:50:54.155 --> 00:50:56.727
Let's find out ourselves.

00:51:04.685 --> 00:51:06.427
Bread this late?

00:51:06.427 --> 00:51:08.658
Bang Geul just dropped it off.

00:51:08.658 --> 00:51:10.258
Have some.

00:51:10.258 --> 00:51:12.927
- She was here? - Yeah.

00:51:30.635 --> 00:51:33.363
<i>Please insert a memory card.</i>

00:51:36.426 --> 00:51:38.005
He's thorough.

00:51:38.972 --> 00:51:41.425
Grandma.

00:51:41.425 --> 00:51:44.632
It's soft and fluffy, right?

00:51:44.632 --> 00:51:46.709
I haven't tried it yet.

00:51:46.709 --> 00:51:49.809
It's even better with milk.

00:51:55.205 --> 00:51:56.855
It's good.

00:51:56.855 --> 00:51:58.932
Oh, it's trash day today.

00:51:58.932 --> 00:52:00.065
I'll take it out.

00:52:00.065 --> 00:52:03.498
Taking out trash is my hobby.

00:52:13.281 --> 00:52:15.074
He's thorough.

00:52:17.873 --> 00:52:20.104
My gosh.

00:52:20.104 --> 00:52:22.231
You scared me.

00:52:22.231 --> 00:52:24.990
Were you going to leave me out?

00:52:28.611 --> 00:52:30.541
What are you doing?

00:52:30.541 --> 00:52:33.887
Come have some pancakes.

00:52:33.887 --> 00:52:36.021
I'm not eating.

00:52:36.021 --> 00:52:38.911
Why not? They're so good.

00:52:38.911 --> 00:52:40.144
Come on out.

00:52:40.144 --> 00:52:41.861
Come on.

00:52:41.861 --> 00:52:44.684
You must be hungry by now. Eat first.

00:52:44.684 --> 00:52:47.250
You'll be surprised how good they are.

00:52:57.804 --> 00:52:59.051
[No Search History]

00:53:09.598 --> 00:53:11.875
Grandma, I brought groceries.

00:53:11.875 --> 00:53:13.395
Good work.

00:53:13.395 --> 00:53:16.482
Jun Hyeon, help her carry those.

00:53:16.482 --> 00:53:19.013
Thank you.

00:53:19.013 --> 00:53:20.468
Over here.

00:53:34.077 --> 00:53:37.156
I was just taking a selfie.

00:53:38.213 --> 00:53:40.599
Just a selfie...

00:54:11.104 --> 00:54:16.062
Replace the Chemicals DX Team's laptops first, then move on to Talent Acquisition.

00:54:16.062 --> 00:54:19.582
They have interviews this afternoon, so support them too.

00:54:29.551 --> 00:54:31.530
What's wrong with you two?

00:54:32.930 --> 00:54:38.029
Jun Hyeon is up to something, but I have no way to find out.

00:54:38.029 --> 00:54:39.405
I can't take this anymore.

00:54:39.405 --> 00:54:41.452
I'll handle it...

00:54:41.452 --> 00:54:43.738
- Hey! - Is this the resignation letter?

00:54:43.738 --> 00:54:48.128
The one Jun Hyeon's been dying to get?

00:54:48.128 --> 00:54:49.433
"Dear Jun Hyeon..."

00:54:49.433 --> 00:54:55.411
"When I first saw you, I knew everything I'd been through had led me to..."

00:54:55.411 --> 00:54:58.101
It's a letter that'll move his heart.

00:54:58.101 --> 00:55:00.457
I rewrote it ten times.

00:55:01.730 --> 00:55:06.501
After all we've been through, do you think he's fine right now?

00:55:06.501 --> 00:55:09.951
He isn't that bad.

00:55:09.951 --> 00:55:13.308
No, he's totally cold-blooded.

00:55:13.308 --> 00:55:15.774
So ruthless.

00:55:16.744 --> 00:55:20.170
Kind of like my dad.

00:55:21.628 --> 00:55:23.272
Bang Geul.

00:55:23.272 --> 00:55:27.013
Chairman Kang cared about you a lot.

00:55:27.013 --> 00:55:28.575
He just couldn't show it.

00:55:28.575 --> 00:55:31.674
He was busy with work. I don't resent him.

00:55:31.674 --> 00:55:33.044
I mean it.

00:55:33.044 --> 00:55:36.397
When he heard you were being bullied,

00:55:36.397 --> 00:55:42.634
He skipped the Daesan Hydrogen Complex opening he'd waited years for and flew to the U.S.

00:55:42.634 --> 00:55:45.367
- Really? - Yes.

00:55:45.367 --> 00:55:48.344
He made those kids cry their eyes out.

00:55:48.344 --> 00:55:51.861
He even made them sign that they'd never bully you again.

00:55:51.861 --> 00:55:55.727
He was still so angry after that.

00:55:56.669 --> 00:56:00.390
So that's why they suddenly changed.

00:56:01.915 --> 00:56:04.699
Then why did he leave without seeing me?

00:56:04.699 --> 00:56:07.678
He was afraid he'd lose his nerve.

00:56:07.678 --> 00:56:10.209
He couldn't leave you there if he saw you.

00:56:10.209 --> 00:56:14.259
And if he brought you back, Jae Gyeong would've tormented you again.

00:56:14.259 --> 00:56:16.058
So he held back.

00:56:16.058 --> 00:56:19.249
He knew everything?

00:56:19.249 --> 00:56:23.067
He was always sorry he couldn't do more for you.

00:56:23.067 --> 00:56:25.690
He thought he was protecting you.

00:56:25.690 --> 00:56:27.867
Not because he didn't love you.

00:56:27.867 --> 00:56:31.548
If he was going to leave like this...

00:56:31.548 --> 00:56:35.221
Why didn't he say anything?

00:56:36.489 --> 00:56:39.149
He always seemed so strict.

00:56:39.770 --> 00:56:41.988
He was just a dad too.

00:56:41.988 --> 00:56:44.661
Why are you crying too?

00:56:45.888 --> 00:56:48.065
Coffee's on me.

00:56:48.065 --> 00:56:49.683
Iced Americano for you. Iced latte for you, right?

00:56:49.683 --> 00:56:51.592
- Right. - Take a break.

00:56:51.592 --> 00:56:54.582
From the cafe out front.

00:56:54.582 --> 00:56:57.705
Extra syrup too, please.

00:57:03.348 --> 00:57:04.413
Mom?

00:57:04.413 --> 00:57:08.203
Bring the bean sprouts when you're done.

00:57:08.203 --> 00:57:10.671
Yes, coming.

00:57:10.671 --> 00:57:13.793
Jun Hyeon has a business trip today.

00:57:13.793 --> 00:57:16.580
Business trip? Where?

00:57:16.580 --> 00:57:21.044
Well... Grandma forgot.

00:57:21.044 --> 00:57:23.761
She said it was somewhere Dae...

00:57:23.761 --> 00:57:26.129
"Dae?"

00:57:26.129 --> 00:57:29.222
Daesan Hydrogen Complex?

00:57:32.172 --> 00:57:35.589
You didn't have to come all the way here.

00:57:35.589 --> 00:57:37.438
Chairman Na hates surprises.

00:57:37.438 --> 00:57:40.771
Sounds like you're the one who doubts me.

00:57:43.792 --> 00:57:45.825
Can you really take it?

00:57:45.825 --> 00:57:49.387
I'll cut the CCTV, then set off the fire alarm.

00:57:49.387 --> 00:57:51.219
Five minutes before the fire trucks arrive.

00:57:51.219 --> 00:57:53.819
I'll take it then. Just wait.

00:57:53.819 --> 00:57:55.604
And don't worry.

00:57:55.604 --> 00:57:59.690
If you're that suspicious, come in with me.

00:58:50.831 --> 00:58:52.581
Not again...

00:58:52.581 --> 00:58:54.857
He's dead.

00:59:03.770 --> 00:59:05.770
[Lee Sang Jae]

00:59:08.564 --> 00:59:11.984
- I said I'd call when... - Bang Geul is there!

00:59:13.504 --> 00:59:14.754
What?

00:59:14.754 --> 00:59:20.408
Mrs. Jo told her. She knows you contacted Taeha too.

00:59:20.408 --> 00:59:23.352
I think Bang Geul found something out.

00:59:23.352 --> 00:59:25.352
What are you talking...

00:59:27.205 --> 00:59:30.099
What the hell are you doing?

00:59:30.099 --> 00:59:32.378
Kang Bang Geul...

00:59:33.932 --> 00:59:37.405
Are you really betraying Jae Gyeong?

00:59:37.405 --> 00:59:39.542
Did you side with Taeha?

00:59:39.542 --> 00:59:42.107
I told you to stay out of this.

00:59:42.107 --> 00:59:44.153
Why are you here?

00:59:51.737 --> 00:59:55.041
What the hell... Are you insane?

00:59:55.041 --> 00:59:57.638
Witnesses must be dealt with.

00:59:57.638 --> 00:59:59.780
Bang Geul!

00:59:59.780 --> 01:00:02.463
Wake up! Are you okay?

01:00:02.463 --> 01:00:04.069
Jun Hyeon!

01:00:12.103 --> 01:00:14.364
Jun Hyeon...

01:00:14.364 --> 01:00:16.779
Bang Geul, are you okay?

01:00:16.779 --> 01:00:18.358
Sir...

01:00:18.358 --> 01:00:20.358
I'm okay.

01:00:36.251 --> 01:00:38.815
We're at the Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

01:00:38.815 --> 01:00:40.708
You should've gone to America.

01:00:40.708 --> 01:00:43.121
You wanted to run. So why did you stay?

01:00:43.121 --> 01:00:46.275
My sweet daughter... Why did I never really see you?

01:00:46.275 --> 01:00:49.961
Even when I pushed you away, you kept smiling at me...

01:00:49.961 --> 01:00:52.270
Wake up. Bang Geul!

01:00:52.270 --> 01:00:53.343
Open your eyes!

01:00:53.343 --> 01:00:55.659
Can't you hear Dad?

01:01:43.490 --> 01:01:46.374
You're still here.

01:01:46.374 --> 01:01:48.220
Jae Seong.

01:02:05.620 --> 01:02:08.161
This is your last chance.

01:02:08.161 --> 01:02:11.352
Do everything you can.

01:02:11.352 --> 01:02:13.019
Got it.

01:02:23.539 --> 01:02:25.216
Father.

01:02:25.216 --> 01:02:27.383
Please.

01:02:27.383 --> 01:02:30.062
Hold on just a little longer.

01:02:35.289 --> 01:02:37.108
Save me!

01:02:46.808 --> 01:02:48.591
Is anyone there?

01:02:48.591 --> 01:02:50.545
I'm trapped in here!

01:02:50.545 --> 01:02:52.915
Is anyone there?

01:02:52.915 --> 01:02:55.255
I'm trapped in here!

01:02:55.255 --> 01:02:57.988
I'm Hwang Jun Hyeon!

01:03:32.981 --> 01:03:34.845
<i>You're in on my revenge.</i>

01:03:34.845 --> 01:03:36.522
<i>So stick with me.</i>

01:03:36.522 --> 01:03:38.537
<i>We found the original footage.</i>

01:03:38.537 --> 01:03:42.091
<i>Let's show the world Na Byeong Mo's filth.</i>

01:03:42.091 --> 01:03:44.848
<i>We have proof of the real killer.</i>

01:03:44.848 --> 01:03:46.775
<i>Call the prosecutors. The police too.</i>

01:03:46.775 --> 01:03:50.246
<i>If you don't want to be on the news, arrest him now.</i>

01:03:50.246 --> 01:03:52.123
<i>Want a fight?</i>

01:03:52.123 --> 01:03:54.264
<i>You think my father will sit back?</i>

01:03:54.264 --> 01:03:57.309
<i>Get rid of him. Make sure he's gone.</i>

01:03:57.309 --> 01:04:00.432
<i>You even had someone killed. Impressive.</i>

01:04:00.432 --> 01:04:02.609
<i>Should we take all of Taeha?</i>

01:04:02.609 --> 01:04:05.027
<i>Can I say what I want now?</i>

01:04:05.027 --> 01:04:08.715
<i>My final target is Kang Jae Gyeong.</i>

